OL,3,C'We're not ordinary, we're
OL,4,Cextraordinary' Three women on their
OL,5,Cfight for justice
OL,7,FThree women who between them have been
OL,8,Ffighting for justice for a total of
OL,9,Fmore than 35 years have been brought
OL,10,Ftogether by ITV Meridian to share
OL,11,Ftheir experiences.
OL,13,FJackie Britton, Jo Hamilton and
OL,14,FShelagh Simmons have all been involved
OL,15,Fin long running campaigns to try and
OL,16,F"right the wrongs of the past."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/21
