OL,3,C'We're not ordinary, we're
OL,4,Cextraordinary' Three women on their
OL,5,Cfight for justice
OL,7,FMeeting for the first time at the ITV
OL,8,FMeridian studios, they all agreed that
OL,9,Ftheir long battles had many common
OL,10,Fthemes including the huge toll it had
OL,11,Ftaken on them all.
OL,13,FAnd they say they've felt dismissed
OL,14,Fand ignored by those in power.
OL,16,F"We're always told lessons will be
OL,17,Flearned, but they never are," said
OL,18,FShelagh.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/21
