OL,3,C'We're not ordinary, we're
OL,4,Cextraordinary' Three women on their
OL,5,Cfight for justice
OL,7,F"The fact that we're here today
OL,8,Ftalking about this means that lessons
OL,9,Fhaven't been learned."
OL,11,FJackie, from Portsmouth, contracted
OL,12,FHepatitis C when she was given a blood
OL,13,Ftransfusion after childbirth by the
OL,14,FNHS. She's been a key witness in the
OL,15,FInfected Blood Inquiry which is about
OL,16,Fto release its final report after five
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/21
