OL,3,C'We're not ordinary, we're
OL,4,Cextraordinary' Three women on their
OL,5,Cfight for justice
OL,7,F"But there is a common theme isn't
OL,8,Fthere - and that's the lack of
OL,9,Fempathy. That's that's what I find it
OL,10,Fquite distressing."
OL,12,FSpeaking about the impact of the
OL,13,Flength of those fights Jackie Britton
OL,14,Fsaid: "For the infected blood, there's
OL,15,Fbeen over 3000 deaths since the 70s.
OL,17,F"It's mentally, physically devastating
OL,18,Ffor all involved families and infected
OL,19,Falike."
