OL,3,C'We're not ordinary, we're
OL,4,Cextraordinary' Three women on their
OL,5,Cfight for justice
OL,7,F"Since we started in 2015, over
OL,8,F270,000 women have died without seeing
OL,9,Fjustice," she said.
OL,11,F"And women have had to sell their
OL,12,Fhomes.They've had to use food banks.
OL,13,FSome have had divorce settlements
OL,14,Fbased on a state pension age of 60.
OL,16,F"You know, there are various and many
OL,17,Fimpacts, and it's all been huge and
OL,18,Fdevastating."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/21
