OL,3,C'We're not ordinary, we're
OL,4,Cextraordinary' Three women on their
OL,5,Cfight for justice
OL,7,F"I'm sure with the amount of evidence
OL,8,Fthat's been put out there, that the
OL,9,Ftruth will come out."
OL,11,FJo Hamilton thinks that the Post
OL,12,FOffice Inquiry will result in people
OL,13,Fbeing held to account.
OL,15,FShe said: "In our case, people have
OL,16,Factually perverted the course of
OL,17,Fjustice, they've committed perjury, so
OL,18,FI do believe there will be people that
OL,19,Fwill be held to account.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/21
