OL,3,C'We're not ordinary, we're
OL,4,Cextraordinary' Three women on their
OL,5,Cfight for justice
OL,7,F"I think they thought that we were a
OL,8,Fgroup of older women who would take it
OL,9,Fand we're not," she added.
OL,11,F"One of our slogans is not going away
OL,12,Fand we're not going away.
OL,14,F"We might be older women, but we're
OL,15,Fstrong older women, we're feisty older
OL,16,Fwomen and we're going to see this
OL,17,Fthrough to the end. We knew it
OL,18,Fwouldn't be quick, we knew it wouldn't
OL,19,Fbe easy, but we're prepared for that,
OL,20,Fand we're in it for the long haul."
