OL,4,Cextraordinary' Three women on their
OL,5,Cfight for justice
OL,7,FIn response, a Post Office
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "Post Office is
OL,9,Fdeeply sorry for the hurt and
OL,10,Fsuffering that has been caused to
OL,11,Fvictims and their loved ones, and we
OL,12,Fare committed to ensuring that they
OL,13,Freceive the justice and redress that
OL,14,Fthey so deserve, with offers of more
OL,15,Fthan #179 million made to around 2,800
OL,16,FPostmasters to date.
