OL,3,C'We're not ordinary, we're
OL,4,Cextraordinary' Three women on their
OL,5,Cfight for justice
OL,7,F"We are dedicated to ensuring the
OL,8,Fwrongs of the past cannot be repeated,
OL,9,Fand we are working to enable the
OL,10,FInquiry to get to the truth of what
OL,11,Fhappened and establish accountability
OL,12,Ffor that."
OL,14,FOn restorative justice a spokesperson
OL,15,Fsaid: "Our Chief Executive and other
OL,16,Fmembers of the senior leadership
OL,17,Fcontinue to meet with people affected
OL,18,Facross the country to apologise
OL,19,Fdirectly and to hear, first hand,
OL,20,Ftheir personal experiences.
