OL,3,C'We're not ordinary, we're
OL,4,Cextraordinary' Three women on their
OL,5,Cfight for justice
OL,7,F"It is important for Nick Read that
OL,8,Fthese meetings take place so that Post
OL,9,FOffice colleagues can understand the
OL,10,Ftrauma people have experienced
OL,11,Fthroughout the Horizon IT Scandal to
OL,12,Fprevent anything like this happening
OL,13,Fagain.
OL,15,F"As of February, around 80 of these
OL,16,Fmeetings have taken place and the
OL,17,Foffer remains open to any victim that
OL,18,Fwishes to take part."
