OL,7,FRegarding costs, A Post Office
OL,8,Fspokesperson added: "Costs reflect the
OL,9,Fhuge scale of the scandal as we
OL,10,Fcontinue to ensure fair redress for
OL,11,Fall victims, and to provide full
OL,12,Fsupport for the Public Inquiry's vital
OL,13,Fwork."
OL,15,FOn the WASPI women, a spokesperson
OL,16,Ffrom the Department for Work and
OL,17,FPensions told ITV Meridian that in
OL,18,F2020 both the High Court and Court of
OL,19,FAppeal found no fault in the actions
OL,20,Fof the Department for Work and
OL,21,FPensions.
