OL,7,FThey added that Post Office and
OL,8,Finfected blood scandals are not
OL,9,Fcomparable to the WASPI complaints.
OL,11,FThe Parliamentary Ombudsman recently
OL,12,Fpublished a report having investigated
OL,13,Fclaims that the Department for Work
OL,14,Fand Pensions failed to provide
OL,15,Faccurate, adequate and timely
OL,16,Finformation about areas of State
OL,17,FPension reform. It found
OL,18,Fmaladministration.
