OL,7,FA DWP spokesperson said: "We will
OL,8,Fconsider the Ombudsman's report and
OL,9,Frespond in due course, having
OL,10,Fcooperated fully throughout this
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,F"The government has always been
OL,14,Fcommitted to supporting all pensioners
OL,15,Fin a sustainable way that gives them a
OL,16,Fdignified retirement whilst also being
OL,17,Ffair to them and taxpayers.
