OL,7,F"The State Pension is the foundation
OL,8,Fof income in retirement and will
OL,9,Fremain so as we deliver a further 8.5%
OL,10,Frise in April, increasing the state
OL,11,Fpension for 12 million pensioners.
OL,12,FThis sees the full rate of the new
OL,13,FState Pension rise by #900."
OL,15,FResponding on the Infected Blood
OL,16,FInquiry, a Government spokesperson
OL,17,Fsaid: "This was an appalling tragedy,
OL,18,Fand our thoughts remain with all those
OL,19,Fimpacted.
