OL,7,F"We are clear that justice needs to be
OL,8,Fdelivered for the victims and have
OL,9,Falready accepted the moral case for
OL,10,Fcompensation.
OL,12,F"This covers a set of extremely
OL,13,Fcomplex issues, and it is right we
OL,14,Ffully consider the needs of the
OL,15,Fcommunity and the far-reaching impact
OL,16,Fthat this scandal has had on their
OL,17,Flives.
